reviewText: I enjoyed the movie.  The cast was exceptionally fine, but the plot was so predictable that it colored my final opinion of the film.  I would recommend watching it just to see Amitabh and Farhan as a team.
Wasn't expecting the Bollywood style musical sequences, but the movie was intriguing,  with some interesting plot twists.  I enjoyed it and would recommend it to others
Good movie after while from Amitabh.
